title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“There is not a finite number, I am sure, but it must be a large number.” [From a review by Laurence Urdang in Verbatim, Winter 1993, page 36. Submitted by Harlan Spore, North Little Rock.]
